    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[ConcurrencyStamp], [r].[CreationTime], [r].[CreatorUserId], [r].[DeleterUserId], [r].[DeletionTime], [r].[Description], [r].[DisplayName], [r].[IsDefault], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[IsStatic], [r].[LastModificationTime], [r].[LastModifierUserId], [r].[Name], [r].[NormalizedName], [r].[TenantId]

    ORDER BY [r].[DisplayName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[Discriminator], [p].[IsGranted], [p].[Name], [p].[TenantId], [p].[RoleId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Description], [t].[DisplayName], [t].[IsDefault], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatic], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name], [t].[NormalizedName], [t].[TenantId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[IsGranted], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[RoleId]
FROM (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[ConcurrencyStamp], [r].[CreationTime], [r].[CreatorUserId], [r].[DeleterUserId], [r].[DeletionTime], [r].[Description], [r].[DisplayName], [r].[IsDefault], [r].[IsDeleted], [r].[IsStatic], [r].[LastModificationTime], [r].[LastModifierUserId], [r].[Name], [r].[NormalizedName], [r].[TenantId]
    FROM [Roles] AS [r]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([r].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([r].[TenantId] IS NULL))
    ORDER BY [r].[DisplayName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[Discriminator], [p].[IsGranted], [p].[Name], [p].[TenantId], [p].[RoleId]
    FROM [Permissions] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[Discriminator] = N'RolePermissionSetting') AND ((@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([p].[TenantId] IS NULL))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]
ORDER BY [t].[DisplayName], [t].[Id]
